Former New England Patriots tight end Aaron Hernandez , 25 , was moved Wednesday to the maximum-security Souza-Baranowski Correctional Center in Shirley , Massachusetts .
Hernandez had been at Cedar Junction prison in Walpole since he was convicted April 15 of killing 27-year-old Odin Lloyd in 2013 .
He was moved on Wednesday to Souza Correctional Center is a state prison .